data.description: Experience easy main-level living in this charming, ranch home. With a large fenced yard and a xeriscaped front lot, maintenance is a breeze. Step into a bright open floorplan with plenty of windows, and enjoy the vaulted ceiling in the living room that flows seamlessly into the kitchen and dining area. Stainless Steel upgraded kitchen appliances    The basement features a huge brick fireplace, creating the perfect cozy atmosphere for those cold winter nights. Additionally, there's a bonus craft room or extra bedroom!    You'll find newer honeycomb blinds in the bedrooms. Storage is abundant, and the large 2-car garage even has a solar-powered exhaust fan to keep it cool, along with a sturdy workbench.    Outside, the backyard deck is ideal for grilling, and the spacious yard is perfect for pets to roam and play. No covenants and extra RV parking make the lot perfect for workspace.
